Terminus
********
   The 8x16 regular and 8x16 bold fonts found in lcdfont.c is the Terminus 8x16
   regular and bld fonts (<http://terminus-font.sourceforge.net/>) version 4.38
   by Dimitar Zhekov <dimitar.zhekov@gmail.com>. The ll2 patch has been applied.
   The Terminus fonts are licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.
   The license is included as OFL.TXT, and is also available with a FAQ at
   <http://scripts.sil.org/OFL>.

8x8 font
********
   The 8x8 regular font found in lcdfont.c is the 8x8 font by John Reeves Hall
   (<http://overcode.yak.net/12>), released as "free to use for any purpose".
